title: Georgia Fowler flaunts her enviable physique in a racy black bikini while lounging around
text:
The Victoria's Secret model recently walked the runway at Paris Fashion Week.

And on Tuesday, Georgia Fowler, 27, flaunted her enviable physique as she lounged around in swimwear.

Taking to Instagram, the New Zealand-born stunner shared a sizzling photo showing off her incredible figure in a barley-there black bikini.

Black to basics! Victoria's Secret model Georgia Fowler flaunts her enviable physique in a racy bikini while lounging around on a timber deck

'Snoozy since 98,' she captioned the racy photograph, which had a retro time-stamped filter.

Georgia struck a pose as she lay on an outdoor timber deck while throwing her arms above her head.

The 27-year-old's hair was slicked back and she let her natural beauty shine as she opted for minimal makeup.

Catwalk queen! Georgia recently returned from France where she stormed the runway at Paris Fashion Week

Georgia's post comes one week after she stormed the catwalk for L'Oreal at Paris Fashion Week.

She channeled 80s glamour as she flaunted her trim waist in a snakeskin corset and a white blouse with puffy sleeve.

Her runnway look was completed with wide leg vinyl trousers and black pointed heel stilettos boots.

Strike a pose: While spending time in France, Georgia kept fans up to date with her adventures by posting photos to Instagram

While spending time in France, Georgia kept fans up to date with her adventures by posting uploads to Instagram.

Shortly after jumping off a plane, the model shared series of snaps of herself walking through the city of love

'Straight off the plane from sweats to suits, on a hunt for a crêpe, and some shoes that cover my toes in this rain,' she captioned the post.
description: The Victoria's Secret model recently walked the runway at Paris Fashion Week.  And on Tuesday, Georgia Fowler, 27, flaunted her enviable physique as she lounged around in swimwear.
authors: Mary Mrad For Daily Mail Australia
